12／01／2008～11／30／2010


計畫書目
連結


Book List
Link


計畫簡介 
本計畫的目的是：在國內各大學現有藏書的基礎上，擴充社會語言學領域的藏書量。我們希望能建構一個具有均衡、完整且有系統性的社會語言學書庫。在這個書庫內，收納了多樣化的子題，包含社會語言學理論、語用學、言談分析、混合語、漢語方言及南島語言學的語言調查、功能語法、語言接觸、語言與文化、語言與認知、區域語言研究、方言共時和歷時語法、語言變異研究、借詞音韻學等。同時，這些子題的書目除了涵蓋中文和英文的相關書籍外，還包括其它語言編寫而成的書籍，如歐洲語言(法文和西班牙語)、亞洲語言(日文和韓文)和亞非洲語言(閃語和庫希特語)等。另外，我們所採購的書籍類型也很多元，如圖書、學位論文和過期期刊。社會語言學書籍主要以英文撰寫為主，但不限於英文。 


Introduction
This projects aims to build up balanced, comprehensive and systematic library holdings of sociolinguistic books upgrading the scope of the present collection in the universities in Taiwan. The collection consists of diverse sub-fields of sociolinguistics such as Theories of Sociolinguistics, Pragmatics, Discourse Analysis, Pidgin, fieldworks on Sinitic and Austronesian languages, Fucntional Grammar, Language Contanct, Language and Culture, Language and Cognition, Geographic Studies on languages, Synchronic and Diachronic Studies of Dialects, Language Variation and Loanword Phonology.The collection embraces sociolinguistic works on Mandarin and English as well as other languages such as European languages (e.g. French and Spanish), Asian languages (e.g. Chinese, Japanese and Korean) and Afroasiatic languages (e.g. Semitic languages and Cushitic languages) in addition to many minor languages. Furthermore, the collection covers a wide range of categories including books, theses/ dissertations and back issues. Sociolinguistic books in this collection are mainly written in but not limited to English.







